          <p><strong>Dear colleague,</strong></p>
          <p>This email is to inform you that we have openings for patients in need of inpatient psychiatric care. </p>
          <h2 style="color: #7aa5b4; font-size: 1.1em;">CURRENT OPEN AVAILABILITY</h2>
          <p><strong>Geriatric Unit - Open Beds Available</strong><br />
            <a href="https://pavilionwp.com/admissions">Learn more about our Geriatric program</a></p>
          <p><strong>Acute Unit - Open Beds Available</strong><br />
            <a href="https://pavilionwp.com/admissions">Learn more about our Acute Adult program</a></p>
          <p><strong>Mood Disorder Unit - Open Beds Available</strong><br />
            <a href="https://pavilionwp.com/admissions">Learn more about our Mood Disorder program</a></p>
          <p>Please respond to this email with any bed access issues.</p>
          <p>Sincerely,<br />
             Eric</p>
