          <h3 style="color: #7aa5b4; margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0;">TDO INFORMATION</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0;"><strong>TDO Hearings</strong><br />
            Mondays at 3:00 p.m.<br />
            Wednesdays, Fridays at 11:30 a.m.</p>
          <p><em>Please note: TDO patients must be admitted by 12:00 p.m. to attend a hearing the following day. Those admitted after 12:00 p.m. will attend the subsequent available hearing. Home CSB Emergency Services will be called at hearing time to attend hearings by phone unless other arrangements have been made in advance between home CSB and Colonial Behavioral Health.</em></p>
        </mj-text>
